raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "hyper" %}
{% set version = "0.7.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "12c82eacd122a659673484c1ea0d34576430afbe5aa6b8f63fe37fcb06a2458c" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 1001
  script: "python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed ."
  entry_points:
    - hyper = hyper.cli:main

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - h2          >=2.4,<3.0,!=2.5.0
    - hyperframe  >=3.2,<4.0
    - rfc3986     >=1.1.0,<2.0
    - brotlipy    >=0.7.0,<1.0
    - enum34      >=1.0.4,<2  # [py2k]

test:
  commands:
    - hyper --help
  imports:
    - hyper

about:
  home: http://hyper.rtfd.org/en/latest/
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'HTTP/2 for Python.'
  dev_url: https://github.com/Lukasa/hyper

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - primozgodec
